Title: Center CXC lever ball valve 15mm
Description: Suitable for use in hot or cold water systems, this Center CB CXC 15mm 16 bar ball valve is lever-operated. A ball valve is a type of quarter-turn valve featuring a hollow, perforated ball that pivots to control the flow of a fluid. The valve is open when the ball's hole is in line with flow and closed when pivoted to 90°. The long lasting reliability of ball valves makes them popular in a wide range of settings.

Title: Center Brass Gate Valve with Red Wheel Handle 22mm
Description: Suitable for use in hot or cold water systems, this Center 22mm gate valve is wheelhead-operated. A multi-turn valve, operation of a gate valve  is carried out via a threaded stem, turning multiple times to change position.
